WEBVTT

00:01:16.779 --> 00:01:18.597
vos iz ayer nomen?

00:01:18.597 --> 00:01:20.437
Gita Radovske

00:01:20.437 --> 00:01:23.267
un vi, ven zent ir geboyrn gevorn?

00:01:22.770 --> 00:01:25.699
in akht un tsvantsikstn, nayntsn akht un tsvantsikstn.

00:01:25.699 --> 00:01:26.540
vu?

00:01:26.540 --> 00:01:27.506
in Kovne

00:01:27.506 --> 00:01:30.676
in Kovne. un vi heyst es oyf litvish?

00:01:30.676 --> 00:01:32.290
KAUNAS

00:01:31.549 --> 00:01:34.801
dos iz, KAUNAS zogt men oyf litvish. gut.

00:01:34.801 --> 00:01:36.812
un vos iz geven ayer meydlishe nomen?

00:01:36.812 --> 00:01:38.744
Karmelek

00:01:38.950 --> 00:01:40.540
un vi hot geheysn ayer tate?

00:01:40.335 --> 00:01:41.381
Maks

00:01:41.475 --> 00:01:42.475
Maks Karmelek?

00:01:42.392 --> 00:01:43.409
Maks Karmelek

00:01:43.608 --> 00:01:44.449
un di mame?

00:01:44.449 --> 00:01:46.199
Khaye Karmelek

00:01:46.199 --> 00:01:48.639
un vos iz geven di mames meydlishe nomen?

00:01:47.744 --> 00:01:48.801
Etkin

00:01:48.801 --> 00:01:50.188
Etkin. gut.

00:01:50.188 --> 00:01:52.733
vos iz geven di tates fakh?

00:01:52.733 --> 00:01:54.119
a shinder.

00:01:54.119 --> 00:01:54.915
a shinder.

00:01:54.915 --> 00:01:56.074
yo, a shinder.

00:01:56.074 --> 00:01:57.336
vu hot er gearbet?

00:01:57.336 --> 00:02:00.904
in MAISTAS, in MAIST-

00:02:00.904 --> 00:02:04.508
un dos iz geven zayn eygene gesheft?

00:02:04.381 --> 00:02:06.461
neyn, a regirungs.

00:02:06.311 --> 00:02:08.847
a regirungs gesheft.

00:02:08.847 --> 00:02:12.336
tsi veyst, gedenkt ir epes vegn der gesheft?

00:02:12.336 --> 00:02:15.518
tsi er iz geven groys, a sakh arbeters?

00:02:15.518 --> 00:02:18.199
ikh halt az s'iz gevezn zeyer groys

00:02:18.199 --> 00:02:19.143
groys, yo.

00:02:19.143 --> 00:02:21.313
un yidn un goyim hobn gearbet dortn?

00:02:20.769 --> 00:02:23.937
yo, yidn un goyim, ye.

00:02:23.937 --> 00:02:27.437
ir hot oder, ir hot keyn shvester tsi brider?

00:02:27.437 --> 00:02:29.710
ikh hob gehat nokh dray shvester.

00:02:30.147 --> 00:02:31.639
vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:02:31.210 --> 00:02:35.063
Dine, Rokhe, un Rive.

00:02:35.063 --> 00:02:36.932
ver iz geven di eltste?

00:02:36.938 --> 00:02:38.506
Dine.

00:02:38.506 --> 00:02:40.268
ven iz zi geboyrn?

00:02:40.268 --> 00:02:43.142
in nayntsn fir un tsvantsikstn, UNK.

00:02:43.142 --> 00:02:44.967
un zi lebt nokh?

00:02:44.779 --> 00:02:46.642
zi lebt in, yo, zi lebt.

00:02:46.642 --> 00:02:47.551
vu?

00:02:47.551 --> 00:02:49.324
in Erets Yisroel.

00:02:49.324 --> 00:02:50.950
un zi hot khasene gehat?

00:02:50.540 --> 00:02:52.039
khasene gehat.

00:02:52.039 --> 00:02:54.245
un vos iz ir nomen yetst?

00:02:54.369 --> 00:02:55.775
 Perets.

00:02:56.664 --> 00:02:59.382
un nokh Dinen iz geven Rokhl

00:02:58.619 --> 00:02:59.710
ikh.

00:02:59.382 --> 00:03:00.361
ir. aykh.

00:03:00.269 --> 00:03:01.824
yo yo, ikh bin.

00:03:01.824 --> 00:03:04.074
un dernokh iz Rokhl?

00:03:04.074 --> 00:03:05.608
ye, Rokhl.

00:03:05.608 --> 00:03:07.409
un zi lebt nokh?

00:03:07.255 --> 00:03:08.869
zi lebt, ye.

00:03:08.869 --> 00:03:10.494
vi heyst zi?

00:03:10.494 --> 00:03:12.494
Rokhl Grun.

00:03:12.494 --> 00:03:14.653
Grun. un vu voynt zi?

00:03:14.653 --> 00:03:17.426
zi voynt itster in Erets Yisroel.

00:03:17.622 --> 00:03:19.524
un ir hot gehat nokh eyn shvester.

00:03:19.324 --> 00:03:22.017
nokh eyn shvester, di yingste.

00:03:22.147 --> 00:03:23.180
vi heyst zi?

00:03:23.063 --> 00:03:24.370
Rive.

00:03:24.370 --> 00:03:25.886
un zi iz, zi iz umgekumen?

00:03:25.710 --> 00:03:27.709
zi iz umgekumen.

00:03:27.767 --> 00:03:29.949
vu un ven, veyst ir?

00:03:29.949 --> 00:03:32.062
in dray un fertsikstn yor

00:03:32.062 --> 00:03:35.858
in gefange lager, in Kovne.

00:03:35.858 --> 00:03:42.108
tsi gedenkt ir ayer shtot ayer heym, vu ir flegt voynen?

00:03:42.108 --> 00:03:44.381
yo, ikh gedenk.

00:03:44.381 --> 00:03:47.108
kh'hob gelebt oyf Druskininker gas.

00:03:47.108 --> 00:03:50.154
der balebos iz gevezn Margoles.

00:03:50.278 --> 00:03:51.032
a yid.

00:03:50.915 --> 00:03:52.438
a yid, ye.

00:03:52.438 --> 00:03:54.404
do, mir hobn gelebt in a

00:03:54.404 --> 00:03:59.074
in a shtub, dos iz nit in APARTMENT nor in a shtub.

00:03:59.074 --> 00:04:00.767
nu

00:04:00.767 --> 00:04:03.041
in a shtub in a hoy- in a hoyz?

00:04:02.242 --> 00:04:03.976
in a hoyz, in a hoyz, ye. in a-

00:04:03.608 --> 00:04:06.108
az ir hot gehat, ir hot fardungen eyn shtub?

00:04:06.108 --> 00:04:09.699
neyn, mir hobn gelebt bay der balebos in a hoyz.

00:04:11.733 --> 00:04:13.733
az ir hot gehat nor eyn tsimer?

00:04:13.733 --> 00:04:15.211
mir hobn gehat

00:04:15.211 --> 00:04:18.244
fir tsimern mit a kikh, ye.

00:04:18.244 --> 00:04:19.381
me- meblirt?

00:04:19.381 --> 00:04:20.471
yo.

00:04:20.471 --> 00:04:24.426
zog mir vi azoy, dertseyl mir a bisl vegn dem, vos gedenkt ir.

00:04:24.426 --> 00:04:26.835
vos ikh gedenk, ikh gedenk di kikh.

00:04:26.835 --> 00:04:29.176
gevezn zeyer a sheyne vayse.

00:04:29.176 --> 00:04:31.540
in gants vays. nu, di

00:04:31.540 --> 00:04:34.074
di tsimern zaynen gevezn zeyer sheyn.

00:04:34.074 --> 00:04:37.290
iz gevezn a tsimer far gest oyftsunemen.

00:04:37.290 --> 00:04:40.733
gevezn zeyer sheyn oysgeputst.

00:04:40.733 --> 00:04:44.221
s'iz gevezn a kinder tsimer; s'iz gevezn a tsimer a

00:04:44.221 --> 00:04:49.801
far oyf far tsatskes tsu, oyf TOYS, zikh tsu shpiln mit di kinder, un a hoyf.

00:04:49.801 --> 00:04:51.699
dos gedenk ikh.

00:04:51.699 --> 00:04:54.199
s'iz geven genug ort far zeks mentshn?

00:04:54.199 --> 00:05:00.505
mir zaynen gevezn finf, yo, zeks mit di dinst iz gevezn zeks, yo, s'iz gevezn ort.

00:05:01.000 --> 00:05:04.557
yo, ir hot gezo-, ir hot gehat a dinst vos hot gevoynt tsuzamen

00:05:03.255 --> 00:05:07.074
yo, mir hobn gehat a dinst, un dernokh iz gekumen

00:05:07.074 --> 00:05:12.529
tsvey mol in yor etlekhe dinstn vashn di vesh gevezn spetsyel.

00:05:12.529 --> 00:05:16.608
dernokh hot mayn foter flegt dingen, m-

00:05:16.608 --> 00:05:20.472
oykhet fun, bakn oyf yontev.

00:05:20.472 --> 00:05:24.983
oysbakn; CAKE un dos, flegt men kumen bakn bay undz.

00:05:24.983 --> 00:05:29.017
un un peysekh flegt men nem- nemen bay mayn

00:05:29.017 --> 00:05:33.960
UNCLE; er hot gehat a eygene PIEKARNIA matse, dortn flegt men bakn matse.

00:05:33.960 --> 00:05:36.290
flegt men brengen undz.

00:05:36.290 --> 00:05:39.278
tsi gedenkt ir di nemen fun di

00:05:39.278 --> 00:05:41.710
fun di bobes un zeydes?

00:05:41.710 --> 00:05:43.221
di kinder?

00:05:43.180 --> 00:05:46.460
neyn, neyn, di di der nomen fun di bobes un di zeydes

00:05:46.460 --> 00:05:48.983
Khane hot men ir gerufn

00:05:48.819 --> 00:05:51.278
Khane, Khane Etkin

00:05:48.983 --> 00:05:50.483
Khane Etkin

00:05:51.278 --> 00:05:52.721
yo, un di

00:05:52.721 --> 00:05:54.562
der zeyde Leybl Etkin

00:05:54.562 --> 00:05:55.638
un Leybl Etkin

00:05:55.499 --> 00:05:57.214
ye

00:05:57.162 --> 00:05:59.621
un dos iz geven fun di mames zayt.

00:05:59.180 --> 00:06:00.322
fun di mames tsad

00:06:00.049 --> 00:06:01.572
un fun tatns zayt?

00:06:01.572 --> 00:06:04.089
hob ikh di gantse tsayt nit gevust

00:06:04.089 --> 00:06:05.589
vayl er hot keynmol nit geredt.

00:06:05.589 --> 00:06:09.099
nor in geto hot er ye dertseylt a bisl, nit keyn sakh.

00:06:09.099 --> 00:06:10.086
vos hot er dertseylt?

00:06:10.054 --> 00:06:14.661
er hot dertseylt az er hot dortn a groyse farmegn geblibn.

00:06:14.661 --> 00:06:15.536
nu

00:06:15.536 --> 00:06:18.042
dernokh hot er dertseylt az er

00:06:18.042 --> 00:06:19.724
az er flegt tsoln

00:06:19.724 --> 00:06:24.418
far Yisroel, ke- kari- KEREN KAYEMET; vi zogt men?

00:06:24.418 --> 00:06:26.285
KEREN KAYEMET, yo.

00:06:26.285 --> 00:06:29.745
nu, un er hot gezogt az er hot gehat

00:06:29.745 --> 00:06:32.348
eyn shvester

00:06:32.348 --> 00:06:35.560
un z'zaynen gevezn dray brider.

00:06:35.560 --> 00:06:37.498
nor eyn bruder

00:06:37.498 --> 00:06:41.162
zey zaynen gevezn shoyn fun di aristokratn, zeyer raykhe.

00:06:41.162 --> 00:06:43.719
iz eyn bruder iz umgekumen.

00:06:43.719 --> 00:06:46.657
er hot in finftn yor gekemft

00:06:46.657 --> 00:06:50.578
vi a komunist, er iz gevezn a ofitsir.

00:06:50.578 --> 00:06:54.401
hot men far- farlorn im, me hot nit gevust vu er iz farfaln gevorn.

00:06:54.401 --> 00:06:57.453
nu, mer hot er nit ge- nit geredt.

00:06:57.453 --> 00:06:59.975
vayl alemol ikh bin gevezn nokh a kind, fleg ikh zogn

00:06:59.975 --> 00:07:04.612
", pape, vu iz dayne eltern?" flegt er mir zogn "ikh bin geborn gevorn fun a shteyn."

00:07:04.612 --> 00:07:07.878
un ikh hob gegleybt.

00:07:07.878 --> 00:07:10.020
er hot keynmol nit geredt.

00:07:10.020 --> 00:07:11.701
vu iz geboyrn ayer tate?

00:07:11.701 --> 00:07:12.684
in Varshe.

00:07:12.684 --> 00:07:14.905
in Varshe. un di mame?

00:07:14.905 --> 00:07:15.817
in Kovne.

00:07:15.817 --> 00:07:16.639
in Kovne.

00:07:16.277 --> 00:07:16.941
ye.

00:07:16.941 --> 00:07:17.719
iz

00:07:17.719 --> 00:07:20.056
vi azoy iz der tate gekumen keyn Kovne?

00:07:20.056 --> 00:07:21.534
er iz antlofn.

00:07:21.534 --> 00:07:26.480
er iz gevorn, er hot zikh gekrigt mit di shvester, tsi vos, me flegt,

00:07:26.480 --> 00:07:29.940
er iz gekumen, ikh gedenk nit vi er hot amol dertseylt in geto

00:07:29.940 --> 00:07:33.365
az er iz gekumen on a, on a ZHIKET.

00:07:33.365 --> 00:07:35.011
un mit di shvester

00:07:35.011 --> 00:07:36.888
iz gezesn mit khavertes.

00:07:36.888 --> 00:07:42.560
un ven er iz arayn, hobn zey genumen oplakhn, "ot iz der komunist iz gekumen"

00:07:42.560 --> 00:07:45.675
hot er im vos geentfert, hot zi im gegebn a fr-

00:07:45.675 --> 00:07:47.684
a klap ibern ponem,

00:07:47.684 --> 00:07:49.967
iz er gevorn in kas, un er iz avek.

00:07:49.967 --> 00:07:51.295
un zey hobn nit gevust.

00:07:51.295 --> 00:07:55.826
zey hobn zikh dervust fun im in nayn un fertsikstn yor.

00:07:55.826 --> 00:07:59.029
durkh a tsaytung.

00:07:59.029 --> 00:08:01.073
er hot keynmol nit dertseylt.

00:08:01.073 --> 00:08:04.480
az far vos iz er gekumen spetsyel in KOVNO?

00:08:04.480 --> 00:08:06.268
er iz antlofn.

00:08:06.268 --> 00:08:13.000
farshtanen, ober far vos spetsyel dafke keyn KOVNO? er hot gehat fraynt tsi ah

00:08:08.639 --> 00:08:10.241
ikh veys nit

00:08:10.241 --> 00:08:13.321
neyn, keynem nit, neyn, neyn.

00:08:13.321 --> 00:08:16.135
neyn. er hot nit gehat keyn fraynt.

00:08:16.135 --> 00:08:18.235
ah az vi alt iz er geven ven er iz gekumen?

00:08:18.108 --> 00:08:21.382
er iz mistome gevezn a yor nayntsn.

00:08:21.382 --> 00:08:24.285
kh'hob nokh di bilder ven er iz nokh yung geven.

00:08:24.285 --> 00:08:27.117
tsi veyst ir vi azoy tate un mame hobn zikh

00:08:27.117 --> 00:08:28.205
ah bakent?

00:08:28.082 --> 00:08:30.356
dos hot mir dertseylt dernokh

00:08:30.356 --> 00:08:33.064
mayn tante in Erets Yisroel.

00:08:33.064 --> 00:08:37.843
az, mayn f- mayn zeyde

00:08:37.843 --> 00:08:44.303
hot gehat a PIEKARNIA, nokh der milkhome, tsu er hot farlorn zey; az zey gevezn raykh, in fertsntn yor zaynen zey antlofn

00:08:44.303 --> 00:08:46.064
un ven zey zaynen gekumen

00:08:46.064 --> 00:08:49.914
zaynen zey shoyn gevezn orem. nor eyn PIEKARNIA.

00:08:49.914 --> 00:08:54.108
un, mit a gesheft tsuzamen.

00:08:54.108 --> 00:08:58.666
zey hobn gelebt oyf Nemuno gas.

00:08:58.666 --> 00:09:00.480
vos iz dortn geven?

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:03.135
oyf Nemuno gas, un mayn mame

00:09:03.135 --> 00:09:06.019
hot gelernt in a rusisher gimnazye.

00:09:06.019 --> 00:09:07.984
far di UNK, yene yorn.

00:09:07.984 --> 00:09:09.860
un ven zi iz gekumen

00:09:09.860 --> 00:09:11.435
hot zi geholfn

00:09:11.435 --> 00:09:13.444
mit, in PIEKARNIA.

00:09:13.444 --> 00:09:15.250
dos iz a PIEKARNIA, ye?

00:09:15.250 --> 00:09:18.374
zi iz gevezn zeyer a sheyne

00:09:18.374 --> 00:09:22.321
un, dortn gevezn tishlekh, un me hot

00:09:22.321 --> 00:09:25.798
gegebn ver es hot gevelt COFFEE,

00:09:25.798 --> 00:09:27.338
CAKE, dos.

00:09:27.338 --> 00:09:29.019
iz gekumen mayn foter.

00:09:29.019 --> 00:09:31.391
un dortn iz gevezn a hotel.

00:09:31.391 --> 00:09:32.737
a MOTEL.

00:09:32.737 --> 00:09:34.870
iz er arayn dortn trinken.

00:09:34.870 --> 00:09:38.852
un er hot derzen mayn mame, un er hot zikh farlibt in ir.

00:09:38.852 --> 00:09:40.259
ober vos mayn f-

00:09:40.259 --> 00:09:43.887
keyner hot nit gevust ver er iz, vayl er hot keyn yidish nit gekent.

00:09:43.887 --> 00:09:48.188
nor er hot geshtudirt in AUSTRIA, hot er geredt nor daytsh.

00:09:48.188 --> 00:09:50.958
un, poylish.

00:09:50.958 --> 00:09:54.781
un er iz, er hot nit oysgezen vi a yid.

00:09:54.781 --> 00:09:57.507
dortn oyfn tishl iz dort a bild.

00:09:57.507 --> 00:09:58.326
eyns

00:09:58.331 --> 00:10:00.534
iz velkhe shprakh hobn zey geredt tsvishn zikh?

00:10:00.445 --> 00:10:03.056
zey hobn geredt poylish.

00:10:03.056 --> 00:10:07.755
nor vi mayn mame hot gekent rusish, hot zi gekent a bisl poylish.

00:10:07.755 --> 00:10:11.649
un dernokh hot, iz er gekumen mayn f-

00:10:11.649 --> 00:10:15.728
gefregt ver du bist, hot er nit oysgezogt.

00:10:15.728 --> 00:10:19.613
nit gezogt. er hot gezogt "ikh bin a yid." mer gornit.

00:10:19.613 --> 00:10:20.896
un dernokh,

00:10:20.896 --> 00:10:22.790
eyn gutn frimorgn,

00:10:22.790 --> 00:10:25.992
zey geyen arayn zey gebn a kuk di mame nito iz.

00:10:25.992 --> 00:10:28.958
zey, er hot ir tsugenumen durkhn fentster.

00:10:28.958 --> 00:10:30.843
un z'zaynen antlofn.

00:10:30.843 --> 00:10:34.692
un ven zey zaynen antlofn iz gevezn zeyer a tragedye vayl,

00:10:34.692 --> 00:10:37.780
s'iz gevezn dan mit a goy iz er iz zi antlofn.

00:10:37.780 --> 00:10:41.763
un mayn bobe hot gemeynt az zi shtarbt avek. iz zi hot azoy geshrien un alts.

00:10:41.763 --> 00:10:44.303
un in a gutn frimorgn krigt zi a briv,

00:10:44.303 --> 00:10:45.693
fun mayn mame.

00:10:45.693 --> 00:10:48.684
un zi shraybt az zi hot oyfgeshtelt a khupe,

00:10:48.684 --> 00:10:51.861
"ober vi ikh bin avek azoy vil ikh kumen."

00:10:51.861 --> 00:10:56.480
nu, di bobe hot zikh derfreyt, zogt zi "kum shoyn, vayl mentshn reydn shoyn."

00:10:56.480 --> 00:10:59.250
un, zi iz gekumen mit mayn foter.

00:10:59.250 --> 00:11:01.029
vos er iz fort a yid.

00:11:01.029 --> 00:11:03.994
er iz a yid, ye, nu nokh,

00:11:04.073 --> 00:11:08.067
ot azoy hobn zey gelebt. un keyn fakh hot er nit gehat.

00:11:08.067 --> 00:11:09.994
vayl er hot shtudirt.

00:11:09.994 --> 00:11:13.736
nor vos, zey hobn shoyn gevelt er zol geyn arbetn.

00:11:13.736 --> 00:11:20.277
vayl mayn f-, mayn bobe hot nit gekent oyshaltn zey; z'zaynen gevezn aleyn nit raykh mit a sakh kinder.

00:11:20.277 --> 00:11:23.094
hot er gezogt, er gedenkt az zey hobn gehat

00:11:23.094 --> 00:11:26.948
boynes. ot derfar veyst ir dem vort boyne? MAISTAS.

00:11:26.948 --> 00:11:28.968
zey hobn gehat zeyer fil.

00:11:28.968 --> 00:11:31.674
in Varshe, z'zaynen gevezn zeyer raykh.

00:11:31.674 --> 00:11:34.185
gedenkt er vi a poyer

00:11:34.185 --> 00:11:38.967
flegt shindn di UNK, on a meser, mit di hent.

00:11:38.967 --> 00:11:43.359
un dos ken er geyn, arbetn, un er iz avek arbetn.

00:11:43.359 --> 00:11:49.121
dernokh iz er gevorn dortn a glavne, ikh veys vos er dortn geven, un hobn geredt lebt zeyer gut.

00:11:49.121 --> 00:11:51.660
bizn fertsikstn yor, farshteyt zikh.

00:11:51.660 --> 00:11:54.514
dertseylt mir vegn der heym, az

00:11:54.514 --> 00:11:59.397
di tat-, di, di mame mitn tatn hobn geredt tsvishn zikh poylish?

00:11:59.397 --> 00:12:01.770
afile ven di kinder zenen geboyrn?

00:12:01.408 --> 00:12:05.151
yo, dakht mir oyf poylish. di mame hot mit undz geredt yidish.

00:12:05.151 --> 00:12:07.439
un der foter poylish.

00:12:07.439 --> 00:12:11.785
er hot nit gekent keyn yidish. ober dernokh hot er genumen reydn yidish.

00:12:11.785 --> 00:12:14.658
er hot zikh oysgelernt.

00:12:14.658 --> 00:12:17.521
un in di gasn

00:12:17.521 --> 00:12:21.131
mit f-, ir hot gehat bloyz yidishe fraynt, tsi andere fraynt?

00:12:20.023 --> 00:12:23.377
nor, far di krig? nor yidishe.

00:12:21.803 --> 00:12:25.981
yo. ir hot nor gehat yidishe fraynt?

00:12:24.096 --> 00:12:25.382
nor yidishe, yo.

00:12:25.981 --> 00:12:29.196
far, veys- far vos nisht keyn goyishe fraynt?

00:12:26.749 --> 00:12:28.068
khavertes

00:12:28.927 --> 00:12:31.512
vayl ikh bin gegangen in a yidishe sh- klas

00:12:31.512 --> 00:12:37.081
un in di gas iz gevezn yidn. un iberhoypt hot men mir nit gelozn fray arumloyfn

00:12:37.081 --> 00:12:38.609
iber di gasn.

00:12:38.609 --> 00:12:42.121
s'iz gevezn bay undz azoy vi mir zaynen gevezn soldatn.

00:12:42.121 --> 00:12:47.393
azoy iz mayn foter gevezn mit undz, vayl di mame iz geshtorbn, es zaynen geblibn fir kleyne kinder.

00:12:47.393 --> 00:12:49.691
iz er gevezn zeyer a shtrenger.

00:12:49.691 --> 00:12:51.229
ven iz di mame geshtorbn?

00:12:51.229 --> 00:12:54.815
in dray un draysikstn yor.

00:12:54.815 --> 00:13:01.370
az, az nokhdem hot ir nisht gekent ah fray loyfn in di gasn?

00:13:00.717 --> 00:13:04.211
neyn. mir hobn genumen shoyn geyn in di gasn

00:13:04.211 --> 00:13:08.241
in fertsikstn yor zaynen mir shoyn gegangen aleyn shoyn, fray.

00:13:08.241 --> 00:13:10.677
mayn shvester flegt mikh firn.

00:13:10.677 --> 00:13:12.957
vayl mir hobn shoyn nit gehat keyn dinst.

00:13:12.957 --> 00:13:16.043
in fertsikstn yor iz undz shoyn gevezn nit azoy gut.

00:13:16.043 --> 00:13:18.535
tsi iz Kovne geven a groyser shtot?

00:13:18.535 --> 00:13:23.492
nit keyn gor groyse, ober nit keyn kleyne, nor zeyer a reyne, sheyne shtot.

00:13:23.492 --> 00:13:26.105
vos iz geven der tsol mentshn, veyst ir?

00:13:26.105 --> 00:13:27.726
gedenk nit, veys nit.

00:13:27.726 --> 00:13:30.049
s'iz geven rov yidn, tsi rov goyim?

00:13:29.366 --> 00:13:31.358
s'iz gevezn yidn un goyim.

00:13:31.358 --> 00:13:32.887
mer yidn tsi mer goyim?

00:13:32.887 --> 00:13:37.371
misht, misht. ober goyim mer. ye, mistome goyim.

00:13:37.371 --> 00:13:40.568
vos gedenkt ir funem shtot, s'iz geven a sheyne shtot?

00:13:40.568 --> 00:13:46.035
a sheyne shtot, sheyne kinos, teaters, yidishe teaters.

00:13:46.035 --> 00:13:48.954
se k- zaynen geven organizatsyes?

00:13:48.954 --> 00:13:51.529
ye, s'iz gevezn

00:13:49.213 --> 00:13:53.716
politishe, tsi tsienistishe?

00:13:53.716 --> 00:13:55.384
s'iz gevezn

00:13:55.384 --> 00:13:59.044
mayn man iz gevezn in SOMEN HATSOER, vi zogt men dos?

00:13:59.044 --> 00:14:00.129
SHOMER HATSAIR, ye?

00:13:59.659 --> 00:14:00.948
yo, er iz gevezn.

00:14:00.971 --> 00:14:03.074
s'iz gevezn BETAR. ikh bin

00:14:03.074 --> 00:14:05.474
in BETAR bin ikh gevezn hot

00:14:05.474 --> 00:14:07.327
me hot mikh farshribn.

00:14:07.327 --> 00:14:13.248
bin ikh gevezn mishtome a por monat gefinen, nor mayn foter hot mikh tsugenumen fun dortn, vayl ikh hob gedarft geyn.

00:14:13.248 --> 00:14:15.741
un er hot nit gevelt mir lozn aleyn geyn.

00:14:15.741 --> 00:14:22.875
un er hot mir gezogt keyn organizatsyes zoln mir nit, zayn. un keyn, yo.

00:14:22.875 --> 00:14:24.886
tsi zaynen geven yidishe tsaytungen?

00:14:24.886 --> 00:14:28.610
ye, s'iz gevezn hayntike nayes.

00:14:28.610 --> 00:14:31.844
ikh gedenk shoyn gornit un nokh a por, ikh gedenk nit.

00:14:31.844 --> 00:14:36.616
hayntike nayes veys ikh vayl mayn shvester flegt leyenen.

00:14:36.616 --> 00:14:41.344
un dertseyl mir vegn di shkheynim. ir hot gevoynt in a yidisher gegnt?

00:14:40.804 --> 00:14:45.557
yo, s- in a yidishe gegent, ye. Margoles iz gevezn undzer balebos.

00:14:45.557 --> 00:14:48.402
oder ir hot nisht gehat keyn goyishe shkheynim?

00:14:48.402 --> 00:14:50.682
nor der shtrozh, vi zogt men, der vos flegt ramen.

00:14:50.682 --> 00:14:51.357
der struzh.

00:14:51.357 --> 00:14:56.287
ye, der s- gevezn a poyl- er hot geredt poylish.

00:14:56.287 --> 00:14:58.956
tsi gedenkt ir, hot ir amol

00:14:58.956 --> 00:15:01.300
gefilt antisemitizm dortn?

00:15:01.300 --> 00:15:04.052
ikh hob perzenlekh nit gefilt.

00:15:04.229 --> 00:15:08.180
hot ir gehert vegn pasirungen?

00:15:06.136 --> 00:15:08.582
ye, o, dos gedenk ikh, ye.

00:15:08.582 --> 00:15:11.167
es iz gevezn vinter, bin ikh gegangen,

00:15:11.167 --> 00:15:14.439
in fertsikstn yor dos gevezn, tsi,

00:15:14.439 --> 00:15:17.172
bin ikh gegangen fun klas,

00:15:17.172 --> 00:15:20.563
un s'iz geve- mir hobn zikh geglitsht oyf di UNK

00:15:20.563 --> 00:15:23.954
oyfn bergl, iz tsugegangen a por shkotsim, un zey hobn geshrien tsu undz,

00:15:23.954 --> 00:15:29.087
"fort in Palestine!" ikh hob nit farshtanen vos iz Palestine.

00:15:29.087 --> 00:15:33.664
bin ikh gekumen in shtub un ikh hob gezogt az me zogt tsu undz "Palestine."

00:15:33.664 --> 00:15:36.459
dos iz shoyn ober in fertsikstn yor.

00:15:35.378 --> 00:15:39.187
neyn, oder dos gevezn ende nayn un draysikstn.

00:15:39.187 --> 00:15:44.270
ober in di frierdike yorn, in di yorn tsvantsik, oder draysik.

00:15:42.458 --> 00:15:43.186
neyn

00:15:44.166 --> 00:15:47.749
neyn, ikh hob keyn zakh nit gefilt.

00:15:44.270 --> 00:15:45.624
fun di frierdike draysik yor.

00:15:47.778 --> 00:15:49.880
nit gefilt.

00:15:49.880 --> 00:15:54.235
un vi azoy hot ir ge- zikh gefirt in der heym mit yidishkeyt?

00:15:54.235 --> 00:15:58.525
ven mayn mame hot gelebt, gedenk ikh az s'iz gevezn

00:15:58.525 --> 00:16:01.091
milkhiks un fleyshiks.

00:16:01.091 --> 00:16:02.606
farshidene keylim?

00:16:02.055 --> 00:16:06.728
ye, dos gedenk ikh. un ikh gedenk az me flegt kumen sukes, fleg ikh zen zi flegt

00:16:06.728 --> 00:16:10.635
davenen, me flegt, zi flegt treyslen di, dem ts-

00:16:10.635 --> 00:16:13.066
ikh veys vi es ruft zikh, di lule-

00:16:12.508 --> 00:16:14.393
der LULAV

00:16:13.564 --> 00:16:14.896
yo, yo.

00:16:14.896 --> 00:16:17.084
nu, un ven zi iz geshtorbn

00:16:17.084 --> 00:16:20.632
iz mayn foter hot gehaltn yidishkeyt, ober farshteyt zikh nit azoy.

00:16:20.632 --> 00:16:25.710
nor vos peysekh gedenk ikh flegt men alts aroystrogn fun shtub farbrenen di khomets

00:16:25.710 --> 00:16:28.795
un ramen un dos gedenk ikh az, yo.

00:16:28.795 --> 00:16:33.678
ober az s'iz geveysn fleyshik un milkhik, dos veys ikh nit.

00:16:33.678 --> 00:16:35.374
fun mayn foter.

00:16:35.374 --> 00:16:38.311
ayer shteyger lebn, tsi iz es geven

00:16:38.311 --> 00:16:43.657
a gute, a hoykhe, a mitldi-, a niderike in farglaykh mit di andere mentshn?

00:16:43.657 --> 00:16:49.207
mir biz dem, bizn fertsikstn yor hobn mir gelebt gut, raykh.

00:16:49.207 --> 00:16:52.524
ikh hob gefil- nor mayn fo- ikh bin gevezn,

00:16:52.524 --> 00:16:55.925
mayn foter hot mir zeyer lib gehat, vayl ikh fleg zeyer,

00:16:55.925 --> 00:16:59.566
ikh bin geven a kind, helfn kinder, oreme.

00:16:59.566 --> 00:17:01.920
mayn fo- shvester nit azoy.

00:17:01.920 --> 00:17:05.922
zi ke- zi flegt kenen gebn a nedove, ober reydn flegt zi nit.

00:17:05.922 --> 00:17:08.785
un ikh fleg gebn. un reydn.

00:17:08.785 --> 00:17:13.177
flegt zayn bay undz zeyer ni- ikh fleg hern vi zi flegt redn tsu mayn foter.

00:17:13.177 --> 00:17:17.560
az zi kh- zi geyt tsu di kinder, tsu di kinder. mayn foter flegt entfern:

00:17:17.560 --> 00:17:23.573
"oreymkeyt iz keyn shande nit, nor me darf zayn a mentsh."

00:17:23.573 --> 00:17:27.381
hob ikh mit ir nit geshtimt di gantse tsayt nit.

00:17:27.381 --> 00:17:31.135
nor vos ikh hob nit getort reydn kegn ir a vort.

00:17:31.135 --> 00:17:33.405
vayl zi iz di elter gevezn far mir.

00:17:33.405 --> 00:17:39.140
ikh hob di gantse tsayt getrakht "ikh'l oysvaksn vel ikh ir gebn UNK"

00:17:39.140 --> 00:17:42.162
tsi iz geven a shpitol, shpitoln?

00:17:42.114 --> 00:17:44.282
ye, s'iz gevezn a yidishe shpitol

00:17:43.772 --> 00:17:44.958
a yidishe shpitol?

00:17:44.282 --> 00:17:47.775
yo, s'iz gevezn a yidishe shpitol, un a zey shpitol, yo.

00:17:47.775 --> 00:17:50.463
vos heyst a yidishe shpitol? mit yidishe doktoyrim?

00:17:48.980 --> 00:17:53.816
yidishe doktoyrim un alts, ye, a UNK gevezn.

00:17:53.816 --> 00:17:59.024
mir flegn geyn, eynmol in monat in UNK me flegt undz kontrolirn.

00:17:59.024 --> 00:18:03.480
di gelungen, rern, dortn gevezn sport.

00:18:03.480 --> 00:18:05.408
yo, s'iz gevezn zeyer gut.

00:18:05.408 --> 00:18:07.688
un sinagogn zaynen geven?

00:18:07.011 --> 00:18:11.124
iz gevezn zeyer sakh UNK, lebn undz iz gevezn dray.

00:18:11.124 --> 00:18:13.070
ir gedenkt vi zey hobn geheysn?

00:18:13.070 --> 00:18:20.918
neyn, bes- mes- bes- beys medresh, un a shul, ikh veys vi dos ober, ikh veys.

00:18:20.918 --> 00:18:23.408
s'iz geven a yidishe besoylem?

00:18:23.408 --> 00:18:25.900
yo. s'iz gevezn a yidishe besoylem.

00:18:26.107 --> 00:18:29.508
hot ir amol geflegt az me zol arayn dortn

00:18:29.508 --> 00:18:32.000
un in farhakn di shteyner.

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:36.000
di matseyves, di goyim? keynmol?

00:18:33.705 --> 00:18:40.042
neyn, keynmol nit, keynmol nit. s'iz gevezn UNK.

00:18:40.042 --> 00:18:46.844
dan iz di yidn zaynen gevezn shtark.

00:18:46.844 --> 00:18:50.050
iz zogt mir, vos iz geshen

00:18:50.050 --> 00:18:52.885
in di yorn finf, zibn

00:18:52.885 --> 00:18:55.183
un draysik, akht un draysik?

00:18:55.183 --> 00:18:57.629
in

00:18:57.629 --> 00:19:02.178
in dray un draysikstn yor gedenk ikh

00:19:02.178 --> 00:19:06.663
iz undzer, der balebos, Margoles

00:19:06.663 --> 00:19:11.694
hot gehat a gesheft fun filfeder.

00:19:11.694 --> 00:19:16.373
er flegt forn in Daytshland brengen.

00:19:16.373 --> 00:19:20.775
iz er in dr-, in fir un draysikstn yor, tsi in finf un draysikstn

00:19:20.775 --> 00:19:24.573
hot zi ge-, hot er gebrakht a fridzhider a kleyner.

00:19:24.573 --> 00:19:25.973
nit keyn groyser.

00:19:25.973 --> 00:19:30.244
un mayn foter hot dos bamerkt, hot er gezogt, er volt dos oykhet gevelt

00:19:30.244 --> 00:19:35.692
me zol mir brengen. vayl es iz geve- di produktn hot men gehaltn in a sklep.

00:19:35.692 --> 00:19:37.063
in a BASEMENT.

00:19:37.063 --> 00:19:42.697
hot er gezogt az er vet forn in akht un draysikstn yor, vet er brengen.

00:19:42.697 --> 00:19:45.366
ven er iz avekgeforn iz er glaykh gekumen.

00:19:45.366 --> 00:19:50.286
vayl er iz gegangen in hotel iz shoyn gevezn ongeshribn "reyn fun JUDEN."

00:19:50.286 --> 00:19:54.863
me hot shoyn nit arayngeladn. un er hot gezogt az s'iz shoyn nit gut.

00:19:54.863 --> 00:20:03.916
un mayn shvester hot geleyent a- di yidishe tsaytung, flegt zi veynen un zogn "pape, gib a kuk vos es tut zikh in Poyln, in Daytshland."

00:20:03.916 --> 00:20:07.168
un dernokh in nayn un draysikstn, flegt er, flegt zi zogn

00:20:07.168 --> 00:20:10.485
"Leyen, gib a kuk ve me mutshet di yidn dortn."

00:20:10.485 --> 00:20:12.014
dos gedenk ikh azoy a bisl

00:20:12.258 --> 00:20:14.256
vayl ikh hob nit geleyent dem tsayt-

00:20:14.478 --> 00:20:18.277
nor zi flegt leyenen. mayn foter hot keyn yidish nit gekent leyenen.

00:20:18.277 --> 00:20:21.891
flegt zi leyenen far im.

00:20:21.891 --> 00:20:24.438
flegt ir amol aroysgeyn fun

00:20:24.438 --> 00:20:26.781
fun KOVNO tsu di arumike shtetlekh?

00:20:26.791 --> 00:20:30.684
ye, ikh, mir hobn gehat a tantn, ikh hob gehat a tante.

00:20:30.684 --> 00:20:36.836
zi hot gelebt hinter kovne in a shtetele Zapishke

00:20:36.836 --> 00:20:41.941
Zapishke, yo. fleg ikh, flegt men mir avekshikn dortn oyf zumer.

00:20:41.941 --> 00:20:44.610
di g- merer, dray fertl

00:20:44.610 --> 00:20:46.805
di shtetl hot gehert tsu zey.

00:20:46.805 --> 00:20:50.354
zaynen gevezn zeyer raykh, gehat eygene velder

00:20:50.354 --> 00:20:55.951
mil, nu, ki, mistome vos far a tsvey hunder ki.

00:20:55.951 --> 00:20:58.773
nu, fleg ikh dort zayn.

00:21:01.983 --> 00:21:07.542
un ir gedenkt flegt ir tsunoyfkumen oftmol mit bobe-zeyde?

00:21:07.542 --> 00:21:09.640
mitn zeydn gedenk ikh nit.

00:21:09.640 --> 00:21:10.531
fun di mames, ye

00:21:10.405 --> 00:21:15.449
fun di mames, ye, ikh gedenk, vayl zi, ikh bin gevezn nokh a kind ven z- er iz geshtorbn, nor dos gedenk ikh az er iz geflegt

00:21:10.601 --> 00:21:11.527
fun di mames, yo.

00:21:15.449 --> 00:21:18.671
peysekh zitsn oyf a kishn.

00:21:18.671 --> 00:21:20.790
hot ir gehat andere kroyvim?

00:21:21.163 --> 00:21:26.768
ye, tantes un, yo, tan- alts fun mayn mames tsad, vayl mayn bobe hot gehat a sakh kinder.

00:21:21.322 --> 00:21:23.661
in KOVNO?

00:21:26.768 --> 00:21:28.723
vi hobn zey geheysn?

00:21:28.723 --> 00:21:34.264
di tantes mit di UNCLES in Kovne, vu sey hobn gelebt?

00:21:34.264 --> 00:21:36.951
eyner iz gevezn Biyomin

00:21:36.951 --> 00:21:44.364
Biyomen, Biyomen, ye.

00:21:38.356 --> 00:21:39.026
Biyomen?

00:21:44.364 --> 00:21:48.098
Shayke hot men im gerufn, Shayke,

00:21:46.164 --> 00:21:46.799
Shayke,

00:21:48.098 --> 00:21:49.516
Yanke,

00:21:49.516 --> 00:21:51.165
Yanke,

00:21:51.165 --> 00:21:53.102
 Bela,

00:21:53.102 --> 00:21:53.769
Bela,

00:21:53.769 --> 00:21:55.362
Leye,

00:21:55.362 --> 00:21:56.613
Bela un Leye.

00:21:56.613 --> 00:21:57.836
un Mine,

00:21:57.836 --> 00:21:59.670
un Mine,

00:21:59.670 --> 00:22:01.617
dakht zikh shoyn dos iz alts.

00:22:01.617 --> 00:22:04.980
vayl a dray zaynen gevezn in Amerike, in Kanade.

00:22:04.980 --> 00:22:06.064
eyne in Amerike.

00:22:06.064 --> 00:22:08.140
dos heyst zey zenen ale geven Etkins?

00:22:08.177 --> 00:22:12.263
ale Etkin, nor vayl zey zaynen gevezn khasene gehat dernokh.

00:22:08.975 --> 00:22:09.757
Etkins

00:22:11.146 --> 00:22:12.637
yo, avade.

00:22:12.263 --> 00:22:16.590
eyne hot men gerufn Blum, di familye, Leye Blum.

00:22:16.590 --> 00:22:19.344
Leye hot khasene gehat, Leye Blum.

00:22:18.628 --> 00:22:23.937
yo, un di yingere gedenk ikh nit di nemen. yo.

00:22:23.937 --> 00:22:27.523
az vos hot ir gezogt, zey, etlekhe fun zey hobn adurkhgelebt

00:22:27.523 --> 00:22:30.803
di milkhome tsi neyn? ale.

00:22:28.125 --> 00:22:30.340
neyn, ale zaynen umgekumen.

00:22:30.340 --> 00:22:34.046
ale umgekumen. ale umgekumen.

00:22:34.046 --> 00:22:36.177
mir hobn nor di bikhele

00:22:36.177 --> 00:22:41.597
UNK der naynter fort vu zey zaynen umgekumen.

00:22:41.597 --> 00:22:44.674
az vos iz geshen in KOVNO

00:22:44.674 --> 00:22:48.510
in akht un draysikstn yor, nayn un draysik?

00:22:48.510 --> 00:22:52.392
keyn zakh nit. keyn zakh, nor me hot gefilt

00:22:52.392 --> 00:22:55.413
ver hot geleyent nor vos tut zikh in Poyln.

00:22:55.413 --> 00:22:58.748
un vi azoy hot, vos hot ir gefilt?

00:22:58.748 --> 00:23:03.733
in Poyln, az me hot UNK, az s'iz dortn, me hot zikh misto-, ikh farshtey nit.

00:23:03.733 --> 00:23:10.821
mayn foter iz gevezn zeyer a kluger, nor ikh farshtey nit vi er hot dos nit farshtanen az do ken zayn di milkhome oykhet in P- in Lite.

00:23:10.821 --> 00:23:13.545
er hot dos, er hot nor ibergelebt

00:23:13.545 --> 00:23:20.991
fun, fun Poyln. vayl er hot dortn gehat di mishp- di, a bruder dortn, kuzins, zaynen ale umgekumen.

00:23:20.991 --> 00:23:25.537
eyne, a shvester mit a bruder, iz gevezn in Amerika avekgeforn.

00:23:25.537 --> 00:23:29.336
un di mame. der foter veys ikh nit, zayner, dos veys ikh nit

00:23:29.336 --> 00:23:34.414
gedenkt ir di nemen fun fun der tates shvester un brider?

00:23:34.414 --> 00:23:38.230
nor fun a eyn shv- fun ey- di shvester, Tsile.

00:23:38.230 --> 00:23:39.205
Tsile.

00:23:39.205 --> 00:23:41.750
ober di nemen fun di brider veys ikh nit.

00:23:41.750 --> 00:23:47.720
ah ye, der kleyner bruder, der yingster hot men gerufn Moyshe, yetst hob ikh zikh dermont. Moyshe.

00:23:47.720 --> 00:23:50.737
Moyshe KARMELIK. Karmelek.

00:23:49.136 --> 00:23:53.995
Karmelek, ye, Karmelek.

00:23:53.995 --> 00:23:57.251
az vos, az ir hot

00:23:57.251 --> 00:23:59.880
d- nor dershpirt durkh di tsaytungen

00:23:59.880 --> 00:24:01.464
in nayn un draysikstn yor?

00:24:01.160 --> 00:24:05.367
ikh, ikh meyn azoy, ikh veys nit tsi ikh hob dan nit farshtanen in gantsn nit,

00:24:05.367 --> 00:24:07.504
nor ikh fleg arayngeyn, fleg ikh hern

00:24:07.504 --> 00:24:11.888
az mayn shvester leyent.

00:24:11.888 --> 00:24:14.737
hob ikh nit farshtanen keyn zakh.

00:24:14.737 --> 00:24:18.442
un vos vayter, iz vos iz geshen in fertsikstn yor?

00:24:18.248 --> 00:24:19.332
in fertsikstn

00:24:18.442 --> 00:24:21.232
ven iz di milkhome gekumen dortn?

00:24:21.232 --> 00:24:23.937
in eyn un fertsikstn, JULY.

00:24:23.937 --> 00:24:26.245
in yuli, in eyn un fertsiks-

00:24:24.803 --> 00:24:29.916
yo, eyn un tsvantsikstn, in eyn un tsvantsikstn tog.

00:24:29.916 --> 00:24:32.646
vos iz geshen?

00:24:32.646 --> 00:24:36.886
azoy. mayn foter flegt shabes nit arbetn.

00:24:36.886 --> 00:24:40.575
er flegt avekgeyn in ovnt arbetn.

00:24:40.575 --> 00:24:42.584
un kumen in der fri.

00:24:42.584 --> 00:24:47.453
zuntik, un zuntik hot er oykhet nit gearbet, vayl dos iz dokh a goyishe UNK

00:24:47.453 --> 00:24:49.505
flegt er oykhet nit arbetn.

00:24:49.505 --> 00:24:51.964
ven er iz gekumen,

00:24:51.964 --> 00:24:55.899
s'iz gevorn aza gefil, un mir zaynen geshlofn,

00:24:55.899 --> 00:24:58.315
hobn mir geshpirt az di bet

00:24:58.315 --> 00:25:00.105
geyt arumet.

00:25:00.105 --> 00:25:01.495
vos hobn mir gemeynt?

00:25:01.495 --> 00:25:03.929
der foter iz gekumen shiker.

00:25:03.929 --> 00:25:06.133
mir hobn nit farshtanen vos tut zikh.

00:25:06.133 --> 00:25:08.931
un mir zaynen aroys fun bet, mir gebn a kuk,

00:25:08.931 --> 00:25:11.475
un mayn foter iz gor nito.

00:25:11.475 --> 00:25:15.555
un dernokh iz er gekumen, iz er mistome gekumen a zeyger

00:25:15.555 --> 00:25:17.463
zeks fun der arbet.

00:25:17.463 --> 00:25:20.677
hobn mir genumen veynen, mir hobn mer tsu shlofn.

00:25:20.677 --> 00:25:26.239
zogt er, me, s'iz milkhome.

00:25:26.239 --> 00:25:29.258
milkhome, un er hot zikh farpakt.

00:25:29.258 --> 00:25:32.285
genumen zayn gants hobn mit di dortn in

00:25:32.285 --> 00:25:35.312
di gold deriker, di gold, di gelt.

00:25:35.312 --> 00:25:37.908
di gelt iz take farfaln gevorn.

00:25:37.908 --> 00:25:40.316
ven es zaynen arayn di rusn geblibn bay d-

00:25:40.316 --> 00:25:44.598
gedenk ikh hob ikh gefinen a zak mit gelt, litn.

00:25:44.598 --> 00:25:54.181
s'iz farfaln gevorn di gelt. not er hot genumen a gantse zekl gold dortn, alts oyf a vel- a rover, oyf a velosiped, dos iz a BICYCLE.

00:25:54.181 --> 00:25:59.548
un mir zaynen gegangen. vu zaynen mir gegangen? oyfn barg tsu mayn tante.

00:25:59.548 --> 00:26:05.358
un ven mir zaynen gegangen hot men undz genumen oyf undz shisn, zenen mir arayn in a shul.

00:26:05.358 --> 00:26:07.159
mir hobn shoyn nit gekent arayngeyn.

00:26:06.672 --> 00:26:07.918
ir redt fun di rusn?

00:26:07.918 --> 00:26:09.275
neyn, far di daytshn.

00:26:09.275 --> 00:26:12.065
in, in eyn un fertsik, di daytshn.

00:26:10.258 --> 00:26:12.845
in eyn un fertsikstn yor, yo.

00:26:12.845 --> 00:26:20.138
un ven mir zaynen arayn bay di, in shul hobn mir gefinen dortn nokh froyen mit mener.

00:26:20.138 --> 00:26:28.194
un, un mir hobn nit gehat vos tsum esn gornit, hot mayn foter gezogt er vet geyn tsurik brengen esn.

00:26:28.194 --> 00:26:30.407
un er hot nit oysgezen vi a yid.

00:26:30.407 --> 00:26:34.240
un er iz avek, nor ven er iz gekumen iz er gevezn zeyer tseshrokn.

00:26:34.240 --> 00:26:35.800
vayl er hot gezogt

00:26:35.800 --> 00:26:37.963
es flegt flien di PULYEs, di

00:26:37.963 --> 00:26:40.617
di di goyim hobn geshosn, nit di daytshn.

00:26:40.617 --> 00:26:43.144
di daytshn zaynen nokh gornit gevezn.

00:26:43.144 --> 00:26:45.102
hobn geshosn

00:26:45.102 --> 00:26:48.520
paze hobn zey, me tor nit aroysgeyn.

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:52.132
zaynen mir gezesn mistome vos a fir teg.

00:26:52.132 --> 00:26:53.921
dernokh zaynen arayn dray

00:26:53.921 --> 00:26:57.399
yunge shkotsim, mit biksn,

00:26:57.399 --> 00:27:00.808
un me hot undz geheysn aroysgeyn.

00:27:00.808 --> 00:27:03.003
ober mir kinder

00:27:03.003 --> 00:27:05.751
hobn mir gedarft krikhn durkhn fentster, durkhn shul.

00:27:05.751 --> 00:27:09.092
un di vider mayn foter, mit di, mayn shvester di eltere

00:27:09.092 --> 00:27:12.085
durkhn tir, nokh mener durkh di tir.

00:27:12.085 --> 00:27:14.604
un mayn shvesterl iz gevezn a kleyninke nokh.

00:27:14.604 --> 00:27:17.461
hot zi gedarft geyn mit di hent in der heykh.

00:27:17.461 --> 00:27:21.438
hobn mit undz avekgeshtelt lebn vant

00:27:21.438 --> 00:27:25.441
un, un me hot gedarft glaykh shisn eynem a yingl.

00:27:25.441 --> 00:27:27.773
a yidisher, mistome a yor fuftsn.

00:27:27.773 --> 00:27:29.672
un ikh hob dos derzen.

00:27:29.672 --> 00:27:32.276
me dertseylt az ikh bin gevezn teyt.

00:27:32.276 --> 00:27:35.439
ikh bin gevezn azoy vays. ikh hob keyn zakh nit farshtanen.

00:27:35.439 --> 00:27:37.239
far vos hobn zey geshosn dem yingl?

00:27:36.948 --> 00:27:38.865
vayl mir zaynen yidn.

00:27:38.865 --> 00:27:42.606
er hot epes geton? stam azoy.

00:27:40.298 --> 00:27:43.105
keyn zakh nit. zey hobn tsuzamen gekhapt.

00:27:43.105 --> 00:27:49.049
un dernokh ven er hot gedarft opshisn dem yat

00:27:49.049 --> 00:27:52.814
iz gekumen tsu loyfn a shi- a poyerte

00:27:52.814 --> 00:27:55.791
fun dortn, vayl zey hobn gelebt dort oyfn barg.

00:27:55.791 --> 00:27:59.633
un zi hot genumen shrayen "far vos shist ir? vos hobn zey geton?"

00:27:59.633 --> 00:28:02.338
"loz zey opet." er hot UNK

00:28:02.338 --> 00:28:05.306
un zey hobn im UNK gelozn

00:28:05.306 --> 00:28:09.291
iz dan zaynen mir gekumen tsurik in shtub.

00:28:09.291 --> 00:28:12.115
mir zaynen gekumen in sht- -urik

00:28:12.115 --> 00:28:16.219
zaynen mir gevezn a tog, tsi tsvey,

00:28:16.219 --> 00:28:21.112
un ikh hob getrogn tey far mayn foter, ikh hob gemakht tey,

00:28:21.112 --> 00:28:26.149
iz gefaln a bombe, vayl mir hobn gelebt oyf UNK lebn taykh.

00:28:26.149 --> 00:28:29.744
un fun yene zayt iz geven di aero- di ar-

00:28:29.744 --> 00:28:33.128
 ikh veys nit vi me zogt oyf yidish

00:28:33.128 --> 00:28:36.478
nu, di, vu di SAMOL- di PLANES lozn zikh arop.

00:28:37.065 --> 00:28:40.885
a fliplats, a fliplats. an erodrom.

00:28:37.978 --> 00:28:46.230
ye, ye, iz dortn a erodrom yo, dortn hot men gevorfn a bombe, bay mir di gloz hot zikh oyfgeheybn bizn

00:28:46.230 --> 00:28:47.578
bizn

00:28:47.578 --> 00:28:52.716
yo, un ikh gib a kuk, UNK di gloz mitamol zikh aropgelozn

00:28:52.716 --> 00:28:56.236
zogt mayn foter "me muz vayter loyfn."

00:28:56.236 --> 00:29:01.375
nu, mir zaynen aroysgelofn ale shkheynim, zaynen gefaln di PULYEs oyf undz alts.

00:29:01.375 --> 00:29:03.478
dernokh zaynen mir gekumen,

00:29:03.478 --> 00:29:05.098
un

00:29:05.098 --> 00:29:06.852
mir zaynen shoyn gezesn in shtub.

00:29:07.255 --> 00:29:08.054
in KOVNO.

00:29:07.497 --> 00:29:08.853
in Kovne.

00:29:08.853 --> 00:29:14.933
nor ikh bin gevezn zeyer a dreyste, kh'hob nit oysgezen vi a yidishe.

00:29:14.933 --> 00:29:18.479
un ikh bin gevezn zeyer a dreyste un mayn foter hot glaykh gezogt "mit eyn kind

00:29:18.479 --> 00:29:20.403
bin ikh shoyn zikher."

00:29:20.403 --> 00:29:23.795
vayl ikh hob zikh anzagt fun esn a sakh.

00:29:23.795 --> 00:29:29.943
tsuker hob ikh shoyn nit genumen, ikh hob gezen az s'iz shver, hob ikh zikh anzagt fun esn, ikh hob genumen esn zeyer veynik.
